Very good game, loads of fun, space for creativity
What a waste. I have a Samsung note 10 plus and the game crashes on startup every time. I'll change my rating if this gets fixes. I was really looking forward for this game too.

Does not matter how many gems or enemies I create it will not let me get pass the creation level literally I click on stuff and tells me whoops we haven't reached this yet WTH Deleting the game. Wish I could give it 0 stars. Seriously the create should not be mandatory. I am officially done with this game. I will never ever ever get any games from this company. Goodbye
replyContent: There is a second step in that tutorial part: setting the channel to 1!

content: Wasn't sure If like this type of game without a controller... Controls are smooth and responsive. Just spent several hours building a level, got sucked in. Great stuff.
Great

Great game! I play it on my Switch and on my phone and tablet. Love that everything syncs. It is fun to play. Great controls. Also great to make you own levels. Good job dev team. Love Crashlands too it is awesome. Just bought that on Switch also. Would recommend others to get LevelHead if you like platformers.

This game has, hands down, the most annoying tutorial I've ever come across. It interrupts constantly. Also, no labels makes things really frustrating and hard to find... Shame, because the gameplay itself is pretty fun. UI is bad, IMO.
Great little platformer that can be a little tough. Plenty of extra player created levels or make your own should you be inclined. Another BScotch gem!

Awesome level builder. B. Shenanigans outdid themselves with this. It's a console/PC level title on mobile that puts games like Mario Maker 2 (the former king of level builders) to shame. Gorgeous graphics, chuckle worthy jokes, catchy soundtrack and most importantly awesome gameplay. I especially like the Tower mechanic where you play to get your levels to the top. Stellar work, seriously. Only gripe is the control scheme. It takes some getting use to, but it is sufficient for most levels.

Way different from what I was expecting! I guess for a platformer...it's unique and difficult. But the colors run together. Everything is really small! It requires A TON of patience! Sorry to say I don't have it for this game! lol!ü•¥
Absolutely amazing platformer with quality a cut above the average mobile game.
I accidentally pressed the deny button, and the game tried to give me a sizure. I tried re-opening the app, and it tried to give me a siezure once again. I uninstalled the app. Why did this happen?
Arcade jumper mixed with social media. Not so much fun.

One of the best game of 2020, Levelhead offers the wonderfully quirky humor Butterscotch Shenanigans is best known for. Essentially it will be your job to train delivery robots by building 2D platforming stages to simulate the shipping dangers of the real world. Really smooth, funny and nice graphics/Cartoon.

Yeah, just buy it. Absolutely top quality games from this developer. If you haven't played it already, crashlands is almost certainly the best thing on the play store. Thanks butterscotch shenanigans for all the polish you give your games. This is another game I'll throw endless hours into.
What an absolute blast, levelhead with it's quirky humor and excellent music, art and gameplay provides a robust platformer with a deep level editor and a friendly community to take part in.
Very fun and responsive with a great sense of humor!
This game is so awesome. Get it.

Levelhead is an outstanding platformer/level creation game! It has solid and fun mechanics, a charming art style, and a robust editing tool to bring your vision to life. Plus, you can link all platforms you play on and enjoy the game everywhere! Great job Butterscotch, Levelhead raises the bar as an excellent, unified game with tremendous value.

Update: Thx so much! This is a gr8 game. I love the gameplay, and also the mixed in humor! I have been waiting 4 it to come out, and it is like a dream come true. (: I wish I could give it 67 1/2 stars!
replyContent: This is already in the game. Check the "Controls" section of the settings page with your controller connected.

content: This is easily one of the smoothest and most satisfying platformers I've ever played on mobile. It has no problems keeping up, the controls are simple and fun, and the game is very obviously deeper than meets the eye. The level editor is quite good and the whole thing can be played for quite a long time. This is one of the good ones.
It's like a cell phone game, but it doesn't suck
Absolutely love this game. Love the cross play between all my devices. Great controls and smart layout for the level builder. Almost easier to build on mobile than desktop.
I LOVE TO MAKE!!!
Love it.

How I wished there was SMM for mobile and now we have SMM for mobile, no, even better than that. The build section is amazing, the game is super optimized as well. The game is super fluid as well. Awesome job devs. A well spent ‚Çπ600!

Fantastic game with great graphics. Levelhead is the best Butterscotch Shenanigans has ever put out; and I say this as a long time fan who's played almost everything they've put out. I highly recommend this for anyone looking for a creative outlet or to simply play an infinite number of fun, exciting levels.

It's like mario maker 2 but on your phone and PC and many other consles, one thing that is bad is that there are no slopes, put slopes in the game and then this is better than mario maker 2. Good job m8!

Perfection in every little detail. The best platformer ever. Couch co-op up to 4 players. What? On mobile? Yeah, on mobile! Sync between all the platforms (PC, Android, iOS, Xbox, Switch). Noooo, can't be. Yeah, can be! You want to play with your little kid? No problem, make a level adjusted to his skills and play. Still have problems? Adjust it even more while playing. Think no more, grab it and play!
A really fun game!

This is brilliant. So polished, so smooth, so humorous... there's just so much content. This game should be like 40 bucks holy moly. If you love platformers don't even hesitate. This has instantly become a classic. Wow!
It's Levelhead, Buy It You Ignorant Genius!!!
Really fun and challenging
Love the game, the smoothness, the music, the jokes, the graphic, controls everything! Highly recommend, a must have!

This game plays, looks and sounds incredible. Platforming feels precise and responsive, the artwork is vibrant and beautiful throughout and the music and effects lift the whole experience even more. This is a must play for creative gamers and platformer fans

Fantastic Platformer! This game is so good. I've tried to play platformers on mobile before and they've fallen short every time because the controls are garbage. You can tell the developers spent a lot of time on the mobile controls of this game and it paid off big time! Aside from that, the level building and sharing mechanics in this game are great and really allow your level to get some exposure. Forget Mario Maker, THIS is the level building game you should be playing!

It's a great platformer with wonderful graphics and sense of humour. Touch controls are great even if sometimes it's not so easy. The fact that the community is very active and the simple way the levels can be shared make this game have no ending. And if you don't like playing others levels, just create your own. The editor is fairly simple but on smartphone it can sometime be too small. If it's your kind of game it should be instantly bought, if not, then buy it and try 2 hours before refund !
I really like this game! It has super tight mechanics engaging levels and a fun and quirky artstyle! I've always loved Butterscotch Shenanigans and they mailed it with this one!
Amazing.

Butterscotch Shenanigans have done it again, a level creating tool with great controls (& gamepad support) and tons of that good ol' BS charm. Another superb entry for mobile gaming from today that know it best.
Very responsive but it likes to crash alot
Control sucks
replyContent: There are some options for changing the controls to better match your device and preferences. Maybe those will help!

content: The cross Platform Mario Maker we need. But better with more robust level building tools.
What can I say? You can make just about any kind of level you want in this game. I think I need some practice because the levels I've been playing that other people have made are so amazing.

Everything is great about the game. Parkour, speedrunning, map making etc. It's all great!!! The controls on the other hand are very confusing and limited in customization I don't understand why there isn't more customization, though this is a great game.
replyContent: If you have ideas for new control schemes and customizations, please let us know in our feedback system! https://www.bscotch.net/feedbag/levelhead

content: Great graphics! Hilarious humor! Awesome game!
It's a great game nothing else to say.
I think this is a great game. It can make me feel the difficult game. I must jump and walk with carefully and use the box to save my way. And take it to my customer hahaha But i love it. Thank you
Love it. Very fun to play levels and build them. The only thing that I believe is missing is controller support.
Fantastic game. Imagine Mario maker with humour. Great cut scenes and an easy to use well thought out editor. Great stuff!
Had to go out of game to set up rumpus, but now we're rockin! If you like the old side scrolling Mario games, you'll love this. Well worth the price!

Amazing game with loads of intresting levels. Also make your own levels with many options available. Mobile controls work flawlessly aswell. Which is hard to achieve with it being a platformer. Get this game now totally worth it!

Another great game! Fun, challenging, and full of character. The level editor is top notch and very easy to use. There is a reason Butterscotch Shenanigans is one of my favorite developers. Kudos, once again!
Intuitive controls and easy level design. I don't like most platformers but this one blew me away
BEST GAME EVER FROM CRASHLANDS DEVS
Amazing game. Touch controls are slightly difficult to get used to, but once you do it's super fun! They did a really good job with this one, perhaps the best mobile game ever.

This game has everything: charming art, a beautiful soundtrack, a campaign mode with a great learning curve, and a lot of variety thanks to the community content. Even the touch controls work surprisingly well after you get some practice.
Making your own levels is very polished! Can't wait to get my friends to play my nonsense levels! Haha
Game platformer paling keren di playstore! Sangat murah dan layak untuk dibeli, yang pengen main Mario Maker tapi versi lebih bagus ya ini solusinya! Langsung aja jangan pikir panjang, beli!

Cut scenes are funny and I them so much. Soundtrack is amazing. Couldn't stop headbanging through the intro part. I usually disable music in games, but not this one, never. Gameplay is so much fun. Controls are well made and movements are fluid. You guys always knew how to make games and I knew this would be a good one just as every other game you guys made. It's worth the wait and my money too.

The game is very responsive and a lot of fun to play! I haven't gotten into the level building mechanic much yet, but really look forward to it! The controls on mobile feel buttery smooth. I do occasionally have trouble accidentally throwing the package instead of jumping, but that'll probably improve with practice! Great devs, great community, great game!
Would put an extra star just for Sam's beautiful singing
This game is amazing. It even works fairly well with touch controls!

Loved this game on PC and it does not disappoint on mobile. The level building on mobile is natural and easy to pick up. It is some solid gameplay with so many options as more and more levels become available butterscotch shenanigans have outdone themselves making a solid platformer level designer game for all platforms.

Another great release from B.S. this is game is pretty cool reminds me a bit of Battleblock Theater or Mario Maker. Platforming and puzzles with comfortable touch controls, lots of options which I really appreciate. Even a UI fix for phones with rounded edges THANK YOU. My only complaint would be occasionally if you go the the edge of a level the character gets hidden behind my thumb and and can be difficult to see.

Build, Share, Package Jump! Looking for a game like Super Mario Maker? Want one that's better? This is your game! You build levels however you want, AND with a sweet community section people will actually play you levels! You have to a big youtube channel to have people enjoy your creations! Check it out! It's a lot of fun!

Super smooth! It's the exact same game you get on consoles and P.C. Nothing cut, everything in all its GLORY at a cheaper price! How can you go wrong? Do yourself a favor, buy it on P.C. and/or your console of choice as well! You can pick up right where you left off on EVERY. SINGLE. DEVICE!

Like another platformer maker game out there that's only on one platform but this one is better and on tons of platforms including the same one as the other game. I'm no level maker but a lover of games with community content and Levelhead handles it better than any game I've ever played. Same for the login system for crossprogression as seen in their previous game Crashlands
Great platformer with lots of options of things to build and solid controls once you get used to them. Great game!
Hilarious madcap fun! The usual Butterscotch humor from Crashlands but with tight platforming controls and a nicer editor than Mario Maker.

I thought this game was gonna be good. Boy was I wrong....it's AMAZING!! The game has the wonderful Butterscotch Shenanigans look and feel with lots of the usual comedy. The character movement and platforming is very smooth and not hard to control(I use a controller) unlike alot of platformers. There is so much potential in the level creator, it's easy to understand how to build and could suit any creative level. Levelhead more than exceeded my expectations and they easily could charge more!
Like Mario Maker, but better, and cross-platform.
